        },
        {
            "title": "港股期指跟外圍反彈 即月期指開報20564點 高水300點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">環球關稅戰暫時略為緩解，近期急回的外圍股市隨即反彈，港股期指今早亦高開。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報20564點，升376點，較上日現貨收市價20264點高水300點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報4850點，升179點，高水161點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報7605點，升103點，高水69點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14843226-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%9f%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8d%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e5%8d%b3%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%a0%b120564%e9%bb%9e-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4300%e9%bb%9e",
