        {
            "title": "長江生命科技今早停牌 暫未悉原因",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長江生命科技(00775)股份今早停牌，暫未悉原因。</p>\n</div>",
